name: Little Does She Know 6
description: Little does she know no one knows what she is made of. Little does she know no one sees her the way she sees herself. Little does she know no paint has been wasted and no color has been wasted on her life when she always felt isolated from the rest of her body. When she looks into the mirror she sees somebody else's life passing her by as she has never knew if her face was her own asset.
